<plot>Metamorphosis captures an intense and exciting period of the young FRANZ KAFKA's life, while he creates his masterpiece The Metamorphosis about a man that wakes up one morning transformed into a gigantic cockroach. When he meets the romantic and idealist Felice, he's quickly caught in an intense and passionate love story that turns his life upside down. The film takes us into the fantastic mind, passion and madness of one of the most influential and important writers in modern literature.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?367117</url></doc>
